prompt_text: Describe the scene of an airport.
content_text: An airport terminal is a busy, very busy place with many passengers coming in and out all the day. There is a constant movement of both people and planes after clearing the security. The passengers head to the waiting area. It is an area of the airport that allows a clear picture of the runway where you can enjoy the airplanes through the glass window. I was sitting at the airport an I saw an aircraft that came. This belongs to Air India and had just landed. So it was quite fast and the sun was setting. It was evening. The company Air India was clearly visible. And part of its wings were raised to slow down. As the aircraft slow down, consider.
